high_descs: Back up, turn to the right, walk to the door straight ahead.
Once you reach the door, turn to the left and face the counter. Pick up the knife
Turn to the left, walk around the island and to the white table in the corner.
Slice half of the bread that is on the table.
Knock two slices of bread onto the floor, turn left and walk over the the counter where the toaster is.
Place the knife on the counter in front of the toaster.
Turn to the right and walk back to the table.
Grab a slice of bread from the table.
Turn to the left and walk to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator,place the bread slice on the shelf, close the door. Open the door, take the slice of bread out of the refrigerator and close the door.
Turn to the left and walk to the stove.
Place the slice of bread on the plate in the microwave that is above the stove.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled bread slice into the microwave.

high_descs: Turn to the right, go forward to the door, turn to the left to face the counter.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go to the end of the counter, go to the right to the wall, turn to the left to face the round table where the bread is.
Cut the bread that is to the left of the salt into slices.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left, go to the counter, turn to the right, go to the counter where the toaster is.
Put the knife down on the counter in front of the toaster.
Turn to the right, go forward, turn to the right, go to the wall, turn to the left to the round table where the bread is.
Pick up a slice of the bread from the table.
Turn to the left, go forward, turn to the left, go forward to the fridge on the right.
Put the bread inside the fridge and close the door, then remove the cold bread from the fridge and close the door.
Turn around, go to the counter, take a right and go forward to the microwave.
Put the bread inside the microwave and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of bread in the microwave.
